Mauritius Bourse to Trade Government Bonds in 2012, Reuters Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-10-13T14:08:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/mauritius-bourse-to-trade-government-bonds-in-2012-reuters-says.html
Mauritius’s stock exchange expects
to introduce trading of government bonds by the first quarter of
2012, Reuters reported, citing an interview with the bourse’s
chief executive officer, Sunil Benimadhu, in Johannesburg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
